PrecisOrder giving notice of the amended National Guideline for REUSABLE UTILITY BAGS (ECP-17-90) requiring that certified reusable utility bags meet a minimum of 300 uses, that they comply with the Canadian General Standards Board standards for colourfastness to rubbing as well as colourfastness and dimensional change in commercial laundering.
